      "content": "i dont even know why im talking to you lol. everything is just so bad. everyone at school saw the clips and now they wont stop tagging me in stuff... people i thought were actually my friends are just laughing at me. i cant even walk down the halls without feeling like everyone is staring and judging. i just want everything to stop. i just want it to be quiet and for none of this to exist anymore.",
