      "content": "it just feels like there's no way out of it. like no matter what i do, the internet keeps moving and the comments keep coming. people are so cruel for no reason. i feel like i'm just stuck in this loop of misery and i can't see a future where this isn't happening. it feels like i'm just waiting for the next thing to break me.",
